theorem Topology.IsOpen_P1_P2_P3_iInter_finite
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {ι : Type _} [Fintype ι] {F : ι → Set X}
    (hF : ∀ i, IsOpen (F i)) :
    Topology.P1 (⋂ i, F i) ∧ Topology.P2 (⋂ i, F i) ∧ Topology.P3 (⋂ i, F i) := by
  classical
  have hOpen : IsOpen (⋂ i, F i) := by
    simpa using isOpen_iInter hF
  simpa using Topology.IsOpen_P1_P2_P3 (A := ⋂ i, F i) hOpen

theorem Topology.P3_subset_closure {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Topology.P3 A → A ⊆ closure A := by
  intro hP3
  dsimp [Topology.P3] at hP3
  intro x hxA
  have : x ∈ interior (closure A) := hP3 hxA
  exact interior_subset this
